original_title: Ang Babae sa Septic Tank 3: The Real Untold Story of Josephine Bracken
overview: “Sequel na, series pa? It’s just a suggestion.” Watch as Eugene Domingo comes full circle as she completes the saga in this third installment of Ang Babae Sa Septic Tank. Witness her in a new light as she tells the real untold story of Josephine Bracken in this iWant original series.
title: The Woman in the Septic Tank 3: The Real Untold Story of Josephine Bracken
